      "content": "A simple formula approach in Excel can be tricky for this specific conditional duplicate check. A more effective method is to use a helper column with a formula like `=COUNTIFS(B:B, B2, C:C, \"pending\")` in column D, starting in D2. Then, you can filter column D for any value greater than 1 to isolate the duplicate emails that meet your criteria.",
