      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That works, thanks. Actually, speaking of spreadsheets and data, I'm also trying to set up an automated screening tool for our HR department to help filter through candidate CVs based on certain criteria. Can you help me draft a set of initial parameters or a logic flow for an AI that would screen for high-potential candidates in supply chain roles?",
